baseline_groups.claim_summary: DEA crackdowns on rogue pain clinic doctors reduce county-level opioid dispensing (MME per capita) using staggered DiD with county and state-by-year FE.
baseline_groups.notes: Single baseline. County + state-by-year FE, county clustering, +/-3 year window, no time-varying controls.

global_notes: 71 specs total. exclude_FL and drop_state_FL are exact duplicates. Several outcome rescalings yield identical t-stats. Heterogeneity interaction specs report treatment effect for reference category, changing the estimand.
